    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i don't mean like getting drunk or anything. i'm talking just one small glass, like maybe 4 or 5 oz? it feels like a tiny amount and it's mostly just for the ritual of relaxing. wouldn't a little bit of alcohol actually help the medication work more effectively to get me to sleep faster? it seems like they both do the same thing anyway.",
